snippet.title: Super Slyder PC Gameplay
snippet.description: Solve puzzles with Slyder and his friends in 288 fun levels! Use Sparky to electrocute Reginald, avoid Unger from touching you, use Boffo as your wall buddy and more! Cute little guy isn't he?
